this variation White has a very clear way of returning the material while
getting a positional advantage.} 13. O-O (13. Bf4 {Followed by 14.d6 is the
most accurate idea.}) 13... Qd6 14. Bf4 Qb4 {A typical square for Black's
queen. Now the exchange doesn't work in White's favour.} 15. Qd1 (15. Qxb4 axb4
